  "commentary": "**DEALER HEDGING COMMENTARY:**\n\nWith SPX at 7100.78 sitting right at the max negative gamma strike of 7110, dealers are currently in buy-the-dip mode and likely providing support here. The PIN regime with massive positive gamma walls at 7150 (+5646M) and especially 7200 (+7355M) creates a strong gravitational pull higher, but dealers will aggressively sell any push toward those levels. Watch for mean reversion back toward the 7150-7200 zone where the heaviest positive gamma concentration will act as a magnet, while the 7110 negative gamma pocket should provide a floor.\n\n**Bottom line:** Expect upward drift toward 7150-7200 with dealers buying this dip and selling any rallies near those levels.",
